name: Hip-Hop
description: Hip-Hop (HPH) is a crypto token available on the Polygon platform (formerly known as Matic) based on the ERC20 standard. Created on 06/29/2023, HPH is closely associated with hip hop culture. The HPH token is a complex for financial support of hip-hop artists, project implementation and creative collaboration in the industry. Owning HPH allows you to participate in the hip-hop ecosystem, earning exclusive rewards and dividends related to the musical and cultural achievements of the hip-hop communities.
